Artificial Intelligence Bot in Golang

Code Explanation
OpenAI Integration: Uses the OpenAI API to send prompts and receive responses.
User Input: The bot reads user input from the terminal and responds based on the response from the OpenAI API.
Conversation Loop: Continues until the user types "exit".
Configuration
Replace "YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY" with your valid OpenAI API key.
Compile and Run:
Compile the code with go build -o chatbot main.go.
Run the bot with ./chatbot.
Testing the Bot
Run the bot and start typing questions or messages into the terminal.
The bot will respond based on the responses generated by the OpenAI GPT API.